        },
        "text_PJxJEe": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>You received the Page of Cups because something within you is softening again. This card appears when emotional openness is returning after a period of guarding, maturity, or self-protection.<\/h3><h3>You may have learned to prioritise logic and always be the one in control. While that has served you well before, you may be distanced from your own wonder or vulnerability. This card is here to tell you that it is safe for you to feel again.<\/h3><h3>You may be starting a new chapter that will be emotional and heavily involve creativity and your intuition. It is important to reconnect with yourself and take on new experiences with sincere displays of self-expression.<\/h3><h3>Your inner world wants attention. It is time to feel those feelings that you had previously postponed or minimised. There is no rush to define anything or commit to nonchalance. <\/h3><h3>Remind yourself that such softness is never a weakness, but a form of intelligence. Look inward, listen to yourself without your own judgement in the way, and open doors you would have never dreamed of before. <br\/><br\/>On Love<\/h3><p>There is hope for new love or renewed intimacy. Your vulnerability could be a welcome gift to someone rather than a heavy risk on your part. <\/p><h3>On Health <\/h3><h3>Stronger emotional health paves the way for improved physical health. Sleep well, let your creativity wander. You will be happier for it. <\/h3><h3>On Money \/ Career <\/h3><h3>You will have new ideas that may not immediately feel practical, or instincts that are not fully formed. It is important you trust these hunches anyway, and see where they lead you. Begin or continue your passion projects quietly but confidently on the side. <\/h3><h3>How to work with this energy<\/h3><p>Stay curious and non-judgemental. Do not rush to define anything, nor attempt to monetise. <br\/><br\/>Recommended products<\/p><ol><li>Sunday Rituals Hair Repair & Growth Oil – Gentle self-care ritual<\/li><li>Berry in Love Bag Charm (Strawberry) –Sweetness & openness<br\/><\/li><\/ol><p>You can find these in our pop-up booth at Night At Orchard, along the outdoor pathway between Ngee Ann City & Ion Orchard between 26-28 Dec, 3pm onwards <\/p>",
            "text_size": "typeset2",
            "secondary_color": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
